description:
Bar, an ordinary middle-aged mister* and a veteran adventurer, lived an easy, comforting life in the Imperial Capital. He would carry items for adventuring parties or help the guild&rsquo;s staff from time to time.
&ldquo;Mr. Bar, glad to have you today!&rdquo;
&ldquo;Thank you for your words.&rdquo;
That uncle who was liked by everyone in the capital, was actually the strongest arsenal of the Empire&ndash;One of the &ldquo;Laevateinn&rdquo;&ndash;Bartolomeus.
&ldquo;Please step forward, Lord Bar.&rdquo;
With a delicate and beautiful elven girl, Welhe Mina, to back him up, his gallant figure racing across the battlefield or the political battleground was simply godly&mdash;like a War God.
The heroic tales of the dowdy adventurer AND the mightiest arsenal starts here!

